# Baseline non-regression fixtures: multi-MB binary outputs and generator
# script used locally / on contributor machines. test-baseline.R auto-skips
# when the directory is absent (see skip_if_no_baseline()), so excluding
# them from the tarball is safe and avoids the CRAN NOTE on file size.
